    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>格式：源代码+未知知识学习</p><p>1.np.array().reshape()</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">house_sizes = np.array([<span class="hljs-number">50</span>, <span class="hljs-number">60</span>, <span class="hljs-number">70</span>, <span class="hljs-number">80</span>, <span class="hljs-number">90</span>, <span class="hljs-number">100</span>, <span class="hljs-number">110</span>, <span class="hljs-number">120</span>]).reshape(-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">output:通过reshape函数，输出一个8×1的二维数组</span><br><span class="hljs-string">[[ 50]</span><br><span class="hljs-string"> [ 60]</span><br><span class="hljs-string"> [ 70]</span><br><span class="hljs-string"> [ 80]</span><br><span class="hljs-string"> [ 90]</span><br><span class="hljs-string"> [100]</span><br><span class="hljs-string"> [110]</span><br><span class="hljs-string"> [120]]</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>.reshape()</code>：是 NumPy 数组（ndarray）的内置方法，用于<strong>改变数组的形状（维度），但不改变数组中元素的总数和元素本身</strong>。</li><li>参数详解：<ul><li>第二个参数<code>1</code>：明确指定数组的<strong>第二维（列数）为 1</strong>。</li><li>第一个参数<code>-1</code>：这是 NumPy 中<code>reshape</code>方法的<strong>特殊占位符</strong>，含义是 “让 NumPy 自动计算该维度的大小”，计算的依据是 “数组总元素数不变”。</li></ul></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    
